
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{ title }}</title>  <style>
    /* Reset some default styles */

    /**
    I HAVE TRIED A LOT TO MAKE CSS WORK FROM STYLE.CSS WHICH WAS INITIALLY IN THE PUBLIC/STYLESHEETS/STYLE.CSS 
    HOWEVER I ALSO CHANGED THE LOCATION AND THE PATH OF THE FILE BUT STILL IT DID NOT WORKED AND THEN I HAD TO
